node.text:
Only one month is left before Goodwood FoS 2019 and we are happy to announce that we will be back this year! Come to see our Fenyr SuperSport in Goodwood from 4th to 7th July!

We made our first appearance in Goodwood in 2018 with our Fenyr SuperSport, 0-100km/h in 2.8s, 980Nm and a top speed of 400km/h. Are you ready to see us back this year? 😜

#WMotors #Fenyr #SuperSport #FenyrSuperSport #Goodwood #FoS #FestivalofSpeed

node.title: W Motors Fenyr SuperSport at Goodwood FoS 2018!
